sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant SPA as React SPA
  participant API as Express API
  participant DB as MongoDB

  alt Email and password
    User->>SPA: Register or login form
    SPA->>API: POST /api/auth/register or /login
    API->>DB: Create or verify User
    API-->>SPA: JWT token
  else Google OAuth
    User->>SPA: Google ID token
    SPA->>API: POST /api/auth/google
    API->>DB: Upsert User by googleId
    API-->>SPA: JWT token
  end

  SPA->>SPA: Store JWT in localStorage
  SPA->>API: Authorization Bearer on protected routes
  API->>API: protect middleware verifies JWT
  API->>DB: Load req.user
  API-->>SPA: Protected resource
